{"tid":2436111,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–肝臟細胞共可分為三個區域","createTime":"2021-03-06T23:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T04:03:48.000Z","uid":38861,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0ac8f15552b13dd481dadd343418df34815bcdc1","tid":2436111,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T23:06:47.000Z","msg":"上集link: 三十秒科學&ndash;被切除90%還有能力回復正常形狀及功能的器官<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2433238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2433238</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GNoALwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGNoALwq.jpg&h=0b1f9998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撇除皮膚的話，肝臟是我們身體最大的器官。<br />\n除再生能力強大之外，肝臟的另外一個特點就是會與我們的體型成正比關係。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）肝臟細胞根據其所在位置，共可分為三個區域(Zone)。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hK757KP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhK757KP.jpg&h=0a3cc447&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三個區域的肝臟細胞在新陳代謝及基因表達上均有顯著的分別。<br />\n譬如說Zone1細胞所獲得的氧氣量比Zone3的為高，Zone1細胞製糖的能力比Zone3的為強。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）在正常情況下，Zone1的肝臟細胞會一直在減少，並由Zone2的細胞繁殖補回所失去的數量，而Zone3的細胞數量則相對上不會有太大變化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XuoEsKT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuoEsKT.jpg&h=8b3bb64d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）當Zone3區域細胞受損的話，Zone1及2區域細胞便會一起繁殖，填補所失去的細胞。<br />\n反之，當Zone1區域細胞受損的話，Zone2及3區域細胞便會一起繁殖，對其作出填補。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J4dtk4W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ4dtk4W.jpg&h=6166fc8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n若果Zone1、2、3細胞一起受損的話，根據老鼠實驗指出(Ref2)，開頭時份將會由Zone1的細胞主導繁殖，數量到達一定程度後，Zone2區域的細胞便會出手幫忙，而Zone3區域細胞在整個回復的過程中所參與的比例則全程偏低。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=ebb75068\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=afb31111\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6387900/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC6387900%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=b6505e46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6387900/</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6532/eabc4346\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F371%2F6532%2Feabc4346&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=0a002b0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6532/eabc4346</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18600221/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F18600221%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f608c1f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/18600221/</a><br />\nRef4:<a href=\"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK421/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK421%2F&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=570ccf56\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK421/</a><br />\nRef5:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6532/887\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F371%2F6532%2F887&d=nX%2BkuNaC9t4xEeYfS0E7bEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=3cae81a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/371/6532/887</a>"},{"pid":"8d8017fe043b016c91fb0271d53c300ac860d309","tid":2436111,"uid":155431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-06T23:40:28.000Z","msg":"💪🏻🥺👍"},{"pid":"5cc2ef1608d7df7480a927ea85ae65ce3c5f1beb","tid":2436111,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T00:34:28.000Z","msg":"最大器官指細胞最多？"},{"pid":"905a82d60fe8cd98f3a7011cab0072131012b199","tid":2436111,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cc2ef1608d7df7480a927ea85ae65ce3c5f1beb","tid":2436111,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T00:34:28.000Z","msg":"最大器官指細胞最多？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T00:37:47.000Z","msg":"指最重"},{"pid":"edf55ed5d8bb0041b6a312a3e40ccc8c6149b2be","tid":2436111,"uid":256215,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T00:42:51.000Z","msg":"原來皮膚係內臟，咁我出街著短袖衫，即係露出內臟，即係超越露出性器官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cd799dcfb8446ef57c7e1541310350ad8c8b5ea","tid":2436111,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"edf55ed5d8bb0041b6a312a3e40ccc8c6149b2be","tid":2436111,"uid":256215,"like":2,"disli